Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.14,0:19:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.21,0:19:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.02,0:19:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
