Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.84,0:19:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.31,0:19:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次给你做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.65,0:20:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.93,0:20:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.21,0:20:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.21,0:20:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.62,0:20:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.16,0:20:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.70,0:20:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.50,0:20:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.44,0:20:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点吓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.51,0:21:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么可爱的人单独一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.98,0:21:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好紧张啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.52,0:21:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.99,0:21:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是讨厌的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.19,0:21:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.40,0:21:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.47,0:21:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.21,0:21:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.14,0:21:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.81,0:21:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.15,0:21:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了   没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.42,0:21:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.42,0:21:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要干杯吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.96,0:21:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.23,0:21:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.43,0:21:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.30,0:21:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.03,0:21:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认识吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.57,0:22:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.71,0:22:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.72,0:22:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.38,0:22:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点老了吧   没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.72,0:22:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.13,0:22:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊，要再来一杯吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.53,0:22:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.87,0:22:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.74,0:22:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前很丑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.87,0:22:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.34,0:22:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有照片吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.61,0:22:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.35,0:22:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.55,0:22:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.01,0:22:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.55,0:22:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.09,0:22:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么时候的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.02,0:22:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.56,0:22:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变了很多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.49,0:22:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.83,0:23:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.30,0:23:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.57,0:23:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.04,0:23:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.17,0:23:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很厉害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.24,0:23:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了，太帅了，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.38,0:23:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个很怀念吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.91,0:23:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.32,0:23:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.39,0:23:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是妈妈啊，等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.92,0:23:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.13,0:23:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.66,0:23:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.93,0:23:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.07,0:23:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要2天，和妈妈出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.27,0:23:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.01,0:23:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2天吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.68,0:23:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.74,0:23:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九州
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.15,0:23:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.75,0:23:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.02,0:23:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.09,0:23:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.09,0:24:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.03,0:24:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.50,0:24:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.70,0:24:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.23,0:24:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.70,0:24:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.77,0:24:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.04,0:24:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.24,0:24:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.11,0:24:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.11,0:24:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.38,0:24:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点    不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.46,0:24:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
