Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.39,0:25:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.26,0:25:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.93,0:25:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.19,0:25:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要去旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.06,0:25:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说了
