Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:02.28,0:26:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要买礼物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.42,0:26:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:06.68,0:26:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.75,0:26:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈说想见你   我也是
