Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.92,0:26:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:43.79,0:26:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:48.86,0:26:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊，这么晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:50.73,0:26:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:54.07,0:26:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（4月26日7：40下午）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.75,0:27:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，现在到家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:16.09,0:27:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊，15分钟左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:22.63,0:27:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:29.57,0:27:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:31.84,0:27:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:06.67,0:28:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:19.88,0:28:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:21.35,0:28:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:24.69,0:28:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:26.16,0:28:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:27.63,0:28:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊
