Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:06.46,0:29:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:09.80,0:29:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:16.47,0:29:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:19.01,0:29:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊
